Xiaomi 14,
exponentially upgraded

Next-generation Leica Optics
Leica Summilux optical lens
Leica 75mm floating telephoto lens
6.36" classic size
Just right for holding in one hand
The size remains classic so it is easy to hold in one hand. A four-curved back casing makes for a smooth round and comfortable hold. It feels incredible in your hand.
Ultra-thin bezel design
Stunning visuals
Perfectly evolved. Using the most advanced FIAA screen wiring technology to integrate the panel via fanout routing within the display area allows the screen frame to be as narrow as 1.61mm for an unimpeded viewing experience.
Xiaomi x Leica Co-engineered
next-generation optical lens
Leica Summilux optical lens
ƒ/1.6 large aperture
Leica’s large aperture Summilux optical lens is synonymous with high-speed lenses, not only capturing plenty of light in low-light environments, but also delivering outstanding color reproduction, contrast, and resolution. The lens unlocks a significant improvement in capture speeds and the large F1.6 aperture allows Xiaomi 14 to obtain the same image brightness with a shorter exposure time. Xiaomi 14's lens can be called Fast Lens.
